This map was created originally by Cleav420

I RECOMMEND DOWNLOADING zm_killbox_dry_v1.

and throught of makeing 1 for ZM Servers.
I know its a small map and not alot in the map but i did a lot to make this map way more fun for zombie mod servers.

I made everything in this map.
So i hope you enjoy this map.

Also the person who started killbox in the hl2dm game.
Great map. 
There are so many killbox maps in hl2dm.
Hope it plays well in css zombie mod as it plays good in hl2dm.




Also if any one likes the few maps i made you can x-fire me @ cleav420
